&lt;li&gt;Lead the engineering strategy for integrating LLMs, agentic workflows and AI-native development practices into Ocrolus products at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive adoption of modern developer productivity tools and AI-augmented engineering workflows across all teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define standards for AI output quality, hallucination control, cost governance and production reliability&lt;/li&gt;
